    Additionaly,

    There are 4 types of access modifier

    1) Public - Accessible from anywhere ->Any class , any package
    2) private - Accessible within the class.This is the most restrictive one
    3) protected - Accessible within the same package ANd by subclasses
    4) default - Accessible only within the same package


